public class HeaterUnitTesterModel
extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.AtomicModel
    The class HeaterUnitTesterModel defines a model that is used to test the models defining the heater simulator.

    Description

    • Imported events: none
    • Exported events: SwitchOnHeater, SwitchOffHeater, SetPowerHeater, Heat, DoNotHeat

    Glass-box Invariants

     invariant       step >= 0

    Black-box Invariants

     invariant       URI != null && !URI.isEmpty()

    Jacques Malenfant
